#: templates/onboarding/dashboard.html
msgid ""
"Work down the path below — some steps tick themselves off as the Grid sees "
"your data, the rest you check off yourself. Lost on a word? The <a "
"href=\"#glossary\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">glossary</a> is at "
"the bottom."
msgstr ""
"아래 경로를 차근차근 진행하세요 — 일부 단계는 Grid가 데이터를 확인하면 자동으로 완료되고, 나머지는 직접 체크하면 됩니다. 모르는 "
"용어가 있나요? <a href=\"#glossary\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">용어집</a>은 "
"맨 아래에 있습니다."

#: templates/onboarding/dashboard.html
msgid "Your journey"
msgstr "당신의 여정"

#: templates/onboarding/dashboard.html
#, python-format
